fields.name: out_MilitaryStatus
fields.expression:
iif (not isnull(CntPrfl_PSU_VeteranBranch__c),'Veteran',
 iif(not isnull(CntPrfl_PSU_ActiveDutyBranch__c),'Active Duty',iif(not isnull(CntPrfl_PSU_Reserve_Duty_Branch__c),'Reserve National Guard',
 iif(not isnull(CntPrfl_PSU_RelatnshiptoMilitarySrvcMember__c)
 and CntPrfl_PSU_RelatnshiptoMilitarySrvcMember__c<>'Self', CntPrfl_PSU_RelatnshiptoMilitarySrvcMember__c , 'No'))))

fields.name: out_Flag
fields.expression: iif((var_PersonEmail=0 And var_SecondaryEmail=0 And var_UaoInvaildEmail=0 And var_UniversityEmail=0), 0,1)

transformations.name: flt_DataFilter
transformations.advancedFilterCondition:
(IsPersonAccount = 1 and ISNULL(PSU_ID__c) and ISNULL(PSU_ID__pc) and ISNULL(PSU_Inside_Track_Group__c)	and
src_PSU_ITK_Qualifier__c = 1	
and (NOT ISNULL(PersonHomePhone) or NOT ISNULL(PersonMobilePhone)) and
PSU_NeutrinoPhoneValid__pc != '0' and out_Flag=0 and PSU_ITK_Qualifier__c =1) or (ISNULL(PSU_Inside_Track_Group__c) and PSU_Inside_Track__pc =1 and src_PSU_ITK_Qualifier__c = 1	)
